data.description: This beautifully maintained home exudes warmth and character from the moment you step foot on the front porch; a perfect place for that morning cup of coffee.  From there, step into the spacious living area, featuring a beautiful masonry fireplace. The open kitchen boasts modern appliances, beautiful marble countertops with center island, and a cozy breakfast nook, making it a chef's delight. The bedrooms are generously sized, providing comfortable retreats for rest and relaxation. Master-on-main offers one-level living and includes a walk-in closet. Upstairs are 2 secondary bedrooms with shared full bath. The lower level includes finished entertainment space, an additional bedroom, and ample storage space with exterior access. As perfect as the front porch is for morning coffee, the back deck offers enjoyable outdoor space the rest of the day; north facing and looking out over a private wooded treescape, even in the dog days of summer, you'll have a cool place to relax or entertain guests. Located in the long established Tanglewood neighborhood, Dons Court offers a peaceful escape from the hustle and bustle, while still being conveniently close to all Mableton has to offer. To the back of the neighborhood is Georgia's Silver Comet Trail! A wonderful asset in its own right, plans to connect to Atlanta's beltline in the near future offer this area so much upward potential! The East-West Connector, just 2 miles to the north, means swift commute times to the rest of the metro. Or stay and enjoy all that Mableton has to offer! Close to Dogwood Golf Club, Sweetwater Park, and Mable House Barnes Amphitheatre. This adorable property will not last long! Don't miss it!
